{"tid":2398203,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"「養魚」想問下我條魚咩事","createTime":"2021-02-07T05:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T12:00:15.000Z","uid":150206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fba6335a58d1e12850210cb82ab76cb76fcb837e","tid":2398203,"uid":150206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"有幾條藍戰狗幼魚身上有出左紅點<br />\n有條今朝仲要死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後發現佢身上既紅點係抹得甩，懷疑係血黎<br />\n有紅點既幼魚已經隔離左<br />\nGoogle過都唔肯定唔到係咩事<br />\n有冇人知係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKH2qT9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKH2qT9.png&h=6efa903d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y32BvkV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy32BvkV.png&h=16b76970&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"296c41b6e44b860ff3838ee1bf02b5d662e33e96","tid":2398203,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>Hemorrhagic septicemia</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nPhysical/Behavioral Signs/Symptoms:<br />\nA variety of different symptoms may occur, though some fish exhibit no external symptoms<br />\nHemorrhaging of internal organs, skin and muscle<br />\nBulging eyes<br />\nBloated abdomens<br />\nBruised-looking, reddish tints to eyes, skin, gills and fins<br />\nOpen sores<br />\nAbnormal behavior<br />\n<br />\nCause:<br />\nInfection that is brought into aquariums by fish already infected with a deadly virus called Viral hemorrhagic septicemia virus (VHSV or VHSv).<br />\n<br />\nTreatment:<br />\nThere is no known cure for this virus. Sometimes treating secondary infections with wide spectrum antibiotics or general use treatments like Tetra Lifeguard&reg; will reduce mortality. Add one tablet Lifeguard to each 5 gallons and treat 5 consecutive days. Remove activated carbon and conduct a partial water change in between treatments.<br />\n<br />\nNote: Always remove activated carbon before administering any treatments."},{"pid":"5c33d8c6a5503e22dc8da5a0a599d587a7b3b095","tid":2398203,"uid":104297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba6335a58d1e12850210cb82ab76cb76fcb837e","tid":2398203,"uid":150206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"有幾條藍戰狗幼魚身上有出左紅點<br />\n有條今朝仲要死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後發現佢身上既紅點係抹得甩，懷疑係血黎<br />\n有紅點既幼魚已經隔離左<br />\nGoogle過都唔肯定唔到係咩事<br />\n有冇人知係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKH2qT9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKH2qT9.png&h=6efa903d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y32BvkV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy32BvkV.png&h=16b76970&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:50:48.000Z","msg":"魚仔唔受得重藥<br />\n唯有落藍藥水<br />\n溫度調高D<br />\n唔好喂嘢食"},{"pid":"81f45b778add84c3d13f9e8446a79f956af4b3f5","tid":2398203,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"自己問佢啦 我地又唔識佢"},{"pid":"81c3b95379605c1576c107760c576a3c22c5729d","tid":2398203,"uid":225696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"去金魚舖問賣魚佬仲快<br />\n但不外乎都係叫你換水滴藥水"},{"pid":"a872b6c3eb67fbe9871a5fa29fba72617895cef1","tid":2398203,"uid":150206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"296c41b6e44b860ff3838ee1bf02b5d662e33e96","tid":2398203,"uid":182180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T06:23:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>Hemorrhagic septicemia</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\nPhysical/Behavioral Signs/Symptoms:<br />\nA variety of different symptoms may occur, though some fish exhibit no external symptoms<br />\nHemorrhaging of internal organs, skin and muscle<br />\nBulging eyes<br />\nBloated abdomens<br />\nBruised-looking, reddish tints to eyes, skin, gills and fins<br />\nOpen sores<br />\nAbnormal behavior<br />\n<br />\nCause:<br />\nInfection that is brought into aquariums by fish already infected with a deadly virus called Viral hemorrhagic septicemia virus (VHSV or VHSv).<br />\n<br />\nTreatment:<br />\nThere is no known cure for this virus. Sometimes treating secondary infections with wide spectrum antibiotics or general use treatments like Tetra Lifeguard&reg; will reduce mortality. Add one tablet Lifeguard to each 5 gallons and treat 5 consecutive days. Remove activated carbon and conduct a partial water change in between treatments.<br />\n<br />\nNote: Always remove activated carbon before administering any treatments."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:44:10.000Z","msg":"唔係掛咁大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能之前細細條陣養得太密 <br />\n跟著突然大得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9593f5dd59bb1f04a3c1e8755a3c004ff7fd895","tid":2398203,"uid":150206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c33d8c6a5503e22dc8da5a0a599d587a7b3b095","tid":2398203,"uid":104297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fba6335a58d1e12850210cb82ab76cb76fcb837e","tid":2398203,"uid":150206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"有幾條藍戰狗幼魚身上有出左紅點<br />\n有條今朝仲要死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後發現佢身上既紅點係抹得甩，懷疑係血黎<br />\n有紅點既幼魚已經隔離左<br />\nGoogle過都唔肯定唔到係咩事<br />\n有冇人知係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" c